column5: These last few years I’ve been really down 6-7 years, probably i know I’m not going to get a good job a good life I wanted to be a pro footballer but I don’t want to kill myself but I don’t want to be in this world I’m lonely, Depressed, I seriously dont get why I’m put on the world cause soon if I can’t cope like I can’t cope today I just wanna end it...
